# Processed-JD archive — keep local only.
# Auto-maintained by scripts/score_jobs.py; useful for personal history but
# would expose which JDs (incl. potentially the recipient's own) have been
# scored if pushed to a public/portfolio repo.
MANUAL_JDS_PROCESSED.md

# Source-of-truth working copies — kept local only.
# These are read by scripts/score_jobs.py at scoring time and contain
# personal/strategic detail (named tier targets, comp expectations, file-pathed
# resume routing). The committed public copies are *_PUBLIC.md, which carry
# the framework / flagship metrics in anonymized form. Per CLAUDE.md Rule 7,
# any framework change here must be reflected in the matching _PUBLIC.md file
# in the same edit.
COMPANY_LIST.md
PROJECT_BRIEF.md

# Personal experience artifacts — keep local only, never push to GitHub
# (PROJECT_BRIEF.md captures the metrics needed by the agent in Ayesha's own words.
#  Local Claude sessions can still read these files for resume/cover-letter work.)
Product Experinces/

# Tweaked-resume repository — local only.
# Used by the asset-match step (Step 2) to give the matcher more candidate
# starting points than just the two top-level base resumes. Contains
# tailored resumes for past applications; not safe to push to a portfolio repo.
Ayesha Resume/Resume to use repository/

# Parallel manual workflow — not part of the job-scraping agent.
# Lives in the project root for convenience only; never push.
London Headhunters/
